{"id":794,"date":"2018-03-28T10:29:43","date_gmt":"2018-03-28T03:29:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/?page_id=794"},"modified":"2018-03-28T10:29:43","modified_gmt":"2018-03-28T03:29:43","slug":"dich-vu-uon-phuc-hoi-toc-hu-ton","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/dich-vu-uon-phuc-hoi-toc-hu-ton\/","title":{"rendered":"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>U\u1ed1n hay u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ecb em ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef khi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c Salon l\u00e0m t\u00f3c t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh. U\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a? T\u1ea1i sao c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, NTM t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1i khuy\u00ean n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u0103ng?<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-571 aligncenter     lazyloaded\" title=\"[Tags]\" src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U%E1%BB%91n-ph%E1%BB%A5c-h%E1%BB%93i_01.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01.png 780w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-300x153.png 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-768x392.png 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-260x133.png 260w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-50x26.png 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-576x294.png 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-147x75.png 147w\" alt=\"U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01 U\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i\" width=\"780\" height=\"398\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01.png\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01.png 780w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-300x153.png 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-768x392.png 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-260x133.png 260w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-50x26.png 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-576x294.png 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01-147x75.png 147w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>KH\u00c1C BI\u1ec6T GI\u1eeeA U\u1ed0N V\u00c0 U\u1ed0N PH\u1ee4C H\u1ed2I T\u00d3C<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>U\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y ra nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho m\u00e1i t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, trong khi u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u00e1i t\u00f3c b\u1ed3ng b\u1ec1nh v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe.<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n u\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u00f3c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00f3c b\u1ecb h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t cho t\u00f3c m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, m\u00e1i t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb g\u00e3y, r\u1ee5ng, x\u01a1 x\u00e1c v\u00e0 l\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o n\u1ebfp. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n.<\/li>\n<li>U\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i gi\u00fap gi\u1eef d\u00e1ng u\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi u\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng.<\/li>\n<li>U\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd r\u1ebb h\u01a1n u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi u\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng. Th\u1eddi gian gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n u\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i s\u1ebd l\u00e2u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi u\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a u\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 ch\u0103m lo cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>4 L\u00dd DO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN HO\u00c0NG H\u1ed2NG \u0110\u1ec2 TH\u1ef0C HI\u1ec6N U\u1ed0N PH\u1ee4C H\u1ed2I<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean s\u00f4 1 Ninh B\u00ecnh<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc cho t\u1eebng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, u\u1ed1n v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<li>Quy tr\u00ecnh nhanh ch\u00f3ng, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i cho m\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-565     lazyloaded\" title=\"[Tags]\" src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th%C3%AAu-ch%C3%A2n-m%C3%A0y_04.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1152px) 100vw, 1152px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04.jpg 1152w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-219x146.jpg 219w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-50x33.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-576x384.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-113x75.jpg 113w\" alt=\"U\u1ed1n-ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i_01 U\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i\" width=\"1152\" height=\"768\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04.jpg 1152w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Phun-th\u00eau-ch\u00e2n-m\u00e0y_04-1024x683.